{"tid":2357202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警大拘捕揭胡志偉未交出所有旅遊證件","createTime":"2021-01-07T09:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T11:20:30.000Z","uid":337888,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9636b00e7e56ddc4976b329b85ad84b5c581eb67","tid":2357202,"uid":337888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:16:54.000Z","msg":"警大拘捕揭胡志偉未交出所有旅遊證件 今解往西九龍法院應訊<br />\n<br />\n【頭條日報】在昨天涉在初選違反國安法的民主黨前主席胡志偉，因早前被控的非法集結案，未有按法庭指令把所有旅遊證件交出，今午將解往西九龍法院應訊。國安處昨晨採取拘捕行動時，在胡志偉住所檢出其他旅遊證件而揭發他違令。<br />\n<br />\n58歲胡志偉被控去年6月30日在中環終審法院外非法煽惑其他身份不詳的人在無合法權限或合理辯解的情況下，明知而參與一個屬未經批准集結的公眾遊行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1969503/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%A4%A7%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95-%E8%AD%A6%E6%90%9C%E5%B1%8B%E6%8F%AD%E8%83%A1%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89%E6%9C%AA%E4%BA%A4%E5%87%BA%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E8%AD%89%E4%BB%B6-%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E6%A1%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1969503%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2590%259C%25E5%25B1%258B%25E6%258F%25AD%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2581%2589%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2597%2585%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BB%25B6-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258F%258A%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A1%2588&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6zwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=476888f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1969503%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2590%259C%25E5%25B1%258B%25E6%258F%25AD%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2581%2589%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2597%2585%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BB%25B6-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258F%258A%2